  "texts": [
    "Therefore, we tested GPT-4 as part of an architecture that is readily deployable from a cost perspective in a real use case.",
    "In addition to the architecture we used in this study, integrating structured EHR data into prompts may further refine the screening process.",
    "This combination strategy enhance the patient pool by not relying exclusively on diagnostic codes, especially for clinical diagnoses such as heart failure.",
    "This approach might broaden the scope of potential candidates and result in a more inclusive and accurate screening process.",
    "As an example, one could use the structured data for chemotherapy obtained from the EHR to determine if a patient is on active chemotherapy and consequently use GPT-4 to determine if the patient is on chemotherapy for an active malignancy."
